name: VIDEO_SOURCE_FIRST_REMOTE_AUDIO_FRAME
description:
Occurs when the SDK receives the first audio frame from a specific remote user.Deprecated:
                    Please use VIDEO_SOURCE_REMOTE_AUDIO_STATE_CHANGED instead.

parameters.uid: The user ID of the remote user.

parameters.elapsed: Time elapsed (ms) from the local user calling videoSourceJoinChannel until the SDK triggers this callback.
